libgen-cli
==========

This is a CLI tool for downloading books from libgen.is. It is built with the
UNIX philosophy in mind, which means it works well with other tools such as awk.

Example:

    libgen-cli java | awk -F'|' '$5 ~ /pdf/ {print $1}' | libgen-cli --download -


Run libgen-cli --help to see other options.

Dependencies
------------

This dependencies are for debian-based systems, you'll have to adapt them to your
own:

    libghc-curl-dev
    libgmp-dev

